    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit remains in peak mechanical synchronicity, with the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous transient response and the double-VANOS system operating within factory tolerances. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with tactile precision, free of synchro wear, and the M-Variable differential lock provides optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive rod bearing replacement. The chassis retains its factory kinematics with fresh bushings and original dampers, while the exterior finish displays exceptional depth and clarity with no evidence of panel oxidation or clear coat failure. This is a turn-key, high-RPM masterpiece for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 43800.0,
